title: Don't miss out... On this gorgeous renovated 1 Bd Centrally located
posting_body: ['To schedule a tour', 'We now book our tour appointments online!', 'Please call or text us at', 'show contact info', 'to self-schedule from your phone!', 'Book your appointment online today or anytime 24/7!', 'Property Description', 'Located in the heart of Pleasant Hill, Ellinwood is a pet friendly community made up of one-bedroom apartment homes in a condominium-quality complex and serene park-like setting.', 'Our newly renovated community features a sparkling swimming pool and spa, BBQ area, fire pit with lounge seating, clubhouse, professional on-site management, laundry facilities and abundant mature landscaping throughout.', 'We’re conveniently situated adjacent to numerous shopping destinations including nearby Crescent Plaza, Sunvalley Shopping Center and Ellinwood Square located immediately next door.', 'Downtown Walnut Creek is also just a short drive away from the property as is the Pleasant Hill BART Station.', 'Visit us today at <URL> for more info.', 'Details', 'A', 'Offered by:', 'Ellinwood Apartments']
